    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――トリエルMC番組、放送一ヶ月前",
      "startTime": 0,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 1.8666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 5
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_11_01-smr001.m4a",
      "text": "いただきま～す！　もぐもぐ……\nう～ん、お出汁がしみしみのお揚げが美味しい～",
      "startTime": 7.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_11_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "すみれ？\nいい匂いだが、一体何を食べているんだ？",
      "startTime": 14.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 18.1814747494
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_11_01-smr002.m4a",
      "text": "あ、{user}さん\nこれは、インスタントのきつねうどんです",
      "startTime": 20.7333339691,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_11_01-smr003.m4a",
      "text": "おうどんのCMの撮影に向けて美味しく食べる練習を\nしてました。でも、本当に美味しいから困っちゃいます",
      "startTime": 27.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 32.740181923
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_11_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "ああ、すみれが子ギツネの役で出演する\nインスタント食品のCMか",
      "startTime": 36.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 38.6591617585
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_11_01-smr004.m4a",
      "text": "はい！　生放送特番だけじゃなく、番組スポンサーの\nCMにまで出られるなんて、凄く嬉しいです",
      "startTime": 43.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_11_01-smr005.m4a",
      "text": "特番とCM両方にトリエルを大抜擢してくれたので\n期待に応えられるように私も頑張らないと！",
      "startTime": 51.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 55.6387309075
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_11_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "そういえば、すみれは正月特番の企画で\nマラソンに挑戦するんだよな？",
      "startTime": 58.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 60.9442862193
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_11_01-smr006.m4a",
      "text": "はい！　生放送中にマラソンをスタートして、放送終了\nまでにスタジオに戻って来られれば挑戦成功です",
      "startTime": 65.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_11_01-smr007.m4a",
      "text": "生放送のトリを飾る企画と言っても過言では\nありません。必ず時間内にゴールしてみせます！",
      "startTime": 72.8818615777,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 76.9537241936
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_11_01-smr008.m4a",
      "text": "……ところで、そのことで折り入って\n相談があるんですけど、いいですか？",
      "startTime": 80.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 83.7164650599
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_11_01-smr009.m4a",
      "text": "マラソンの練習なんですけど、今は仕事の合間の\n空いた時間にジムで走ってるんです",
      "startTime": 87.8666641235,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_11_01-smr010.m4a",
      "text": "でも、それだけだと練習量が足りなくて……出来れば\nまとまった練習時間を確保して外で走りたいんです",
      "startTime": 95.8999974568,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 100.3133358637
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_11_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "練習時間の確保か……\n分かった、俺の方でスケジュールを調整してみるよ",
      "startTime": 103.3666641235,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 107.0065284728
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_11_01-smr011.m4a",
      "text": "ありがとうございます！　あっ、それと\n実はもう一つお願いがあるんですけど……",
      "startTime": 112.1999974568,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_coast-01.m4a",
          "delay": 6412.313574399988,
          "startTime": 118.6123110312
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――数日後",
      "startTime": 117.4123111407,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_coast-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "3d_corridor_night",
      "startTime": 118.4789776961
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_11_01-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "スケジュールをやりくりして練習時間を作ったが……\n本当に練習の付き添いが俺でいいのか？",
      "startTime": 123.2137365296,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_11_01-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "俺は陸上は素人だから、もっとマラソンに詳しい人に\n見てもらった方がいいと思うが……莉央さんとか",
      "startTime": 130.4666641235,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_11_01-smr012.m4a",
      "text": "そんなことありません！　練習の付き添いは絶対\n{user}さんがいいです！",
      "startTime": 139.0666641235,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_11_01-smr013.m4a",
      "text": "お兄ちゃんがそばで\n応援してくれるだけで、凄く頑張れるんです！",
      "startTime": 142.0666641235,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_11_01-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "そ、そうか……\nまぁ、それですみれがやる気になるなら……",
      "startTime": 147.7333307902,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_11_01-smr014.m4a",
      "text": "ありがとうございます！　今日はこの海岸沿いを\n走るので、自転車で先導をお願いします",
      "startTime": 154.2556221882,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_11_01-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "了解だ。だが、どうして星見市の海岸なんだ？\n走るなら都内でも良かったんじゃないか？",
      "startTime": 162.6333307902,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_11_01-smr015.m4a",
      "text": "ランニングするならここがいいよって\n雫ちゃんと千紗さんがアドバイスしてくれたんです",
      "startTime": 168.0666641235,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_11_01-smr016.m4a",
      "text": "月ストもサニピも……星見プロのアイドルは\nみんなここでトレーニングしたからって……",
      "startTime": 174.7666641235,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_11_01-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "星見プロ伝統のランニングコースか……\n確かにみんなここを走ったな。月ストも、サニピも……",
      "startTime": 181.572084777,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_11_01-smr017.m4a",
      "text": "そういうことなので、私も星見プロのアイドルとして\n伝統のコースを走破してみせますよ～！",
      "startTime": 190.9629416262,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_11_01-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "気合い十分だな。じゃあ、早速練習を始めようか\n俺は自転車をレンタルしてくるから、少し待っててくれ",
      "startTime": 199.7333307902,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_11_01-smr018.m4a",
      "text": "待って下さい\n実はもう自転車は用意してあるんです",
      "startTime": 205.4333307902,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_11_01-smr019.m4a",
      "text": "ここで練習するって言ったら、遙子さんが\n星見市の寮にあった自転車を貸してくれたんです",
      "startTime": 212.0333307902,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_11_01-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "……その自転車って、もしかしてあそこに停めてある\n後部座席に大きな旗が立っているやつか？",
      "startTime": 219.1140050292,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_11_01-smr020.m4a",
      "text": "はい！『星見プロ、天下御免！』と大きく書かれた\nのぼりが立っている自転車です！",
      "startTime": 227.3999974568,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
